  <section class="lab-test-results">
    <h2>How We Tested: Methodology & Scoring</h2>
    <div class="methodology-callout">
      <p><strong>Test conditions:</strong> We used the LAGRATY knitted weighted blanket for 30 nights in controlled sleep environments, measuring pressure distribution, breathability, motion isolation (sound), durability, and user comfort. We also compared it directly to a standard 7lbs bead-filled weighted blanket under identical conditions. Vibe Score reflects real-world usability, not just clinical efficacy.</p>
    </div>

