      <p>The LAGRATY knitted weighted blanket is a smart engineering solution to weighted blanket design. It trades pressure intensity for silence, breathability, and aesthetic appeal. At $290, it's expensive—but if you sleep hot, have pets in bed, hate crunching sounds, and weigh under 160 lbs, it's genuinely excellent. The yarn-weight construction is clever and durable. You're not paying for hype; you're paying for a real design improvement that most people don't even realize they need.</p>
